menu "MagNET Vitals — Status LED"

config CRAW_LED_GPIO
    int "GPIO for the WS2812 status LED"
    default 1
    help
        GPIO connected to the kit's onboard WS2812 (single addressable RGB
        LED). Default 1 matches Seeed's LightRGB example for the XIAO
        ESP32-C6 mmWave kit (`pixelPin = D1` → GPIO 1).

endmenu
